title: Observation of Lee Sin over the last year
body:
If hes on your team and ganks early, you often win the match.

If he decides to not do any early ganking, it has been a nearly 100% loss.

Anyone else see this happening in their matches?

replies.body: Isn't this most junglers though? especially early game junglers. If they don't apply map pressure than it's going to be a hard win.
